name: Adjustable_5-shelf_Bookcase
reviews: Bookcase is sturdy and easy to assemble.
description:
Organize all your books to meet your personal needs with the adjustable five-shelf bookcase. Pick the color that best complements your office or home, and then choose the finish and height of the bookcase to match your existing furniture. Protected with laminate MDF, this bookcase is easy to clean and durable.
